summary:
SET - Skyrim Enhanced Textures 

This mod adds all the best textures, from the best texture packs, together. Try it out! You might get a little FPS drop, not much but if you run a low-end pc, this mod maybe isn\'t something for you. =P
descriptionHtml:
SET - Skyrim Enhanced Textures 

This mod adds all the best textures, from the best texture packs, together. Try it out! You might get a little FPS drop, not much but if you run a low-end pc, this mod maybe isn\'t something for you. As far as I know no bugs with other mods. If you already have a texture pack installed, when it asks you to overwrite TEXTURES, just say yes to all. Just add it to NMM and istall it! Have fun! ;)
author: HeadcrabSucker
